What is consumer/producer problem?

. producer produces data
. consumer consumes data
. they share common resource, that is buffer
. producer produces data when the buffer is not full
. consumer consumes data as long as the buffer is not empty
. producer sleeps if the buffer is full and consumer sleeps if the buffer is empty
. the consumer is notified and woken up (if sleeping) when the producer produces the data
. the producer is notified and woken up (if sleeping) when consumer consumes the data
---


